node.text: Wow looks good lei.. my gal won't let me experiment again, for sure

I wanted to try this haircut hack for a long long time. Finally find the courage to do so.... on her hair 🤪 She had her last haircut in Feb so she definitely needs a trim before returning to school tomorrow. Looking at how pretty the layering turns out, I might try this on myself soon.

Please pardon the background noise. I didn’t plan for her speak in front of the camera. But she’s such a pro! She is so natural and cute. Can she be trained to be the next generation YouTuber?
